<p>Command for getting all the new zettels created in a week.
Wills-Laptop:~ will$ find ~/Dropbox/zettelkasten/<em>.md -mtime -8 ! -name “◆</em>”| egrep ‘20200809|20200808|20200807|20200806|20200805|20200804|20200803’ | wc -l</p>

